[{"id":"VH927162","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><include href=\"../Passage/VH926750.qti.xml\" xmlns:xi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude\"></include></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">¿Qué figura retórica se emplea con la repetición de “¡Oh sol!” (versos 10 y 39) ?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH927162_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div class=\"stimulus_reference\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"><div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"poetry style:1\"><div class=\"title\"><p class=\"title_line passage-title\">Al Sol</p><p class=\"title_line passage-title\">Himno</p></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_1\"></span>Para y óyeme, ¡oh sol!, yo te saludo</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>y extático ante ti me atrevo a hablarte:</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Ardiente como tú mi fantasía,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Arrebatada<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">1</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">arrebatado: precipitado, impetuoso</span></span> en ansia de admirarte</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">5</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Intrépidas a ti sus alas guía.</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¡Ojalá que mi acento poderoso,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Sublime resonando,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Del trueno pavoroso</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>La temerosa voz sobrepujando<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">2</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">sobrepujar: sobrepasar; exceder</span></span>,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">10</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¡Oh sol!, a ti llegara</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y en medio de tu curso te parara!</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¡Ah! Si la llama que mi mente alumbra</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Diera también su ardor a mis sentidos;</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Al rayo vencedor que los deslumbra,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">15</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Los anhelantes ojos alzaría,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y en tu semblante fúlgido<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">3</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">fúlgido: brillante</span></span> atrevidos,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Mirando sin cesar, los fijaría.</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¡Cuánto siempre te amé, sol refulgente!</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¡Con qué sencillo anhelo,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">20</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Siendo niño inocente,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Seguirte ansiaba en el tendido<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">4</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">tendido: extendido</span></span> cielo,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y extático te vía<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">5</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">vía: veía</span></span></span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y en contemplar tu luz me embebecía!</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>[…]</span><br/></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_1\"></span><span class=\"focus_start focus_id:VH926750_1 itemref:VH927286\" id=\"VH926750_1\"></span>¿Y habrás de ser eterno, inextinguible,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">25</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Sin que nunca jamás tu inmensa hoguera</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Pierda su resplandor, siempre incansable,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Audaz siguiendo tu inmortal carrera,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Hundirse las edades contemplando</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y solo, eterno, perenal, sublime,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">30</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Monarca poderoso, dominando?<span class=\"focus_end focus_idref:VH926750_1\"></span></span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>No; que también la muerte,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Si de lejos te sigue,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>No menos anhelante te persigue.</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¿Quién sabe si tal vez pobre destello<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">6</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">destello: resplandor vivo y efímero, ráfaga de luz</span></span></span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">35</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Eres tú de otro sol que otro universo</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Mayor que el nuestro un día</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Con doble resplandor esclarecía!!!</span><br/></div><div class=\"verse\"><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_1\"></span>Goza tu juventud y tu hermosura,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>¡Oh sol!, que cuando el pavoroso día</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">40</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Llegue que el orbe estalle y se desprenda<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">7</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">desprenderse: desunirse</span></span></span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>De la potente mano</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Del Padre soberano,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y allá a la eternidad también descienda,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Deshecho en mil pedazos, destrozado</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\">45</span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Y en piélagos<span class=\"footnote\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"footnote_mark\">8</span><span class=\"footnote_text\">piélago: mar</span></span> de fuego</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Envuelto para siempre y sepultado;</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>De cien tormentas al horrible estruendo,</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>En tinieblas sin fin tu llama pura</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Entonces morirá: noche sombría</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Cubrirá eterna la celeste cumbre:</span><br/><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"line_number badge badge-inverse\"> </span><span class=\"indent indent_0\"></span>Ni aun quedará reliquia de tu lumbre!!!</span><br/></div><span class=\"mandatory_credit_block\"><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">José de Espronceda</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">Obras Completas</span></span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">Madrid: Atlas, 1954.</span><span class=\"mandatory_credit_line\">(Se publicó originalmente en 1834).</span></span></div></div></div>"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Hipérbaton</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Epíteto</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Apóstrofe</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Aliteración</p>"],"answer":2}]